Package org.odpi.openmetadata.fvt.opentypes.model

Class OmTypeFilter

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.fvt.opentypes.model.OmTypeFilter
public class OmTypeFilter extends Object
This stores the types in maps - so they can be accessed easily. This class can be used as a filter to restrict the types that are used for generation.
